<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>11</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zài zhè duǎn zàn de xiāng jù zhōng, dì xiōng nǐ yòu yào qǐ chéng,
 zài zhè duǎn zàn de xiāng jù zhōng, dì xiōng nǐ yòu yào qǐ chéng,
 nán shě nán fēn, lèi zài xīn zhōng liú;
 yuàn wǒ men hěn kuài hěn kuài de zài jiàn miàn;
 yuàn zhǔ zhù fú nǐ duō duō bǎo zhòng.
 nǐ liǎn shàng guà zhe de shì shèng lì xiào róng.
 qián fāng rèn zhòng dào yuǎn, lù tú bù píng.
 sì hǎi wèi jiā zài fēng yǔ zhōng, wǒ men jīn rì fēn bié
 sì hǎi wèi jiā zài fēng yǔ zhōng, liú lèi sā zhǒng de bì
 hé shí xiāng féng? yuàn zhǔ yǔ nǐ tóng xíng!
 huān hū shōu gē, jīn nián yòu shì yī gè hǎo shōu chéng!</lyrics>
<title>dì xiōng nǐ yòu qǐ chéng 迦南11</title>
</song>